OL,3,CWho is responsible for the Summerland
OL,4,Cdisaster?
OL,6,FWho were the main parties involved?
OL,8,FDouglas Corporation owned the land
OL,9,FSummerland was built on, and the
OL,10,Ffacility was leased out to someone who
OL,11,Fwould manage it and complete the
OL,12,Finternal fittings.
OL,14,FThe principal architect was local man,
OL,15,FJames Lomas, with Leeds firm Gillinson
OL,16,FBarnett as the associate architects
OL,17,Fand Alan Theaker as the senior project
OL,18,Farchitect. Trusthouse Forte were
OL,19,Fcontracted to run the building.
OL,21,FHow did the fire start?
