OL,3,CWho is responsible for the Summerland
OL,4,Cdisaster?
OL,6,FThe fire was sparked by three young
OL,7,Fboys from Liverpool who were smoking
OL,8,Fin a small disused kiosk at around
OL,9,F7:30pm.
OL,11,FA discarded cigarette caused the kiosk
OL,12,Fto catch fire, which then fell against
OL,13,Fthe wall, which in turn set alight and
OL,14,Fthe fire spread to the internal wall.
OL,16,FWhat role did the Architects play?
OL,18,FThe inquiry found the primary cause of
OL,19,Fthe blaze was non-fire resistant
OL,20,Fmaterials within the building of
OL,21,FSummerland.
