OL,3,CWho is responsible for the Summerland
OL,4,Cdisaster?
OL,6,FDiscussing the disaster in parliament,
OL,7,F, the MP for Ellesmere Port and
OL,8,FNeston, said: "The architects of
OL,9,FSummerland had opted to use Galbestos
OL,10,Fin its construction.
OL,12,F"Galbestos is a plastic-coated metal
OL,13,Fcladding with limited fire resistance
OL,14,Fand, in combination with the use of
OL,15,Fdecalin, which burns rapidly, for the
OL,16,Finternal walls, created the perfect
OL,17,Fcocktail for a disaster.
