OL,3,CWho is responsible for the Summerland
OL,4,Cdisaster?
OL,6,F"The fire broke through the highly
OL,7,Fcombustible surface and burned
OL,8,Fundetected for a whole 10 minutes
OL,9,Fbefore bursting into the ground floor
OL,10,Fof the leisure building, igniting the
OL,11,FOroglas acrylic panels used on the
OL,12,Fwalls and roof.
OL,14,F"The open-plan design aided the spread
OL,15,Fof the fire, with the internal spaces
OL,16,Facting as chimneys to spread the fire.
