OL,3,CWho is responsible for the Summerland
OL,4,Cdisaster?
OL,6,F"The terror that those in the building
OL,7,Fmust have felt is unthinkable;
OL,8,Fsurvivors described mass panic, with
OL,9,Fthe building appearing to melt before
OL,10,Ftheir eyes."
OL,12,FThe SFC concluded the architects made
OL,13,Fa number of errors which led to the
OL,14,Ftragedy, but 'no villains' were
OL,15,Fsingled out.
OL,17,FThere was also no evidence to suggest
OL,18,Fthe architects had considered fire
OL,19,Fprecautions or any means of escape
OL,20,Fduring the building process.
