OL,3,CWho is responsible for the Summerland
OL,4,Cdisaster?
OL,6,FWhat did building management do?
OL,8,FThe inquiry found that no fire alarm
OL,9,Fsounded when Summerland was engulfed
OL,10,Fin flames and some of the fire escapes
OL,11,Fwere locked - leading to a major delay
OL,12,Fin the evacuation.
OL,14,FOne of the firefighters who was first
OL,15,Fon the scene, said the staff were
OL,16,Ftrying to put the fire out for half an
OL,17,Fhour before the service was called,
OL,18,Fand those in the control room did not
OL,19,Fknow what they were doing.
OL,21,FWhat have the Government done?
